(())

Backtrack and explore other paths:

()()

Final result:

["(())","()()"]
6️⃣ Recursion Tree Idea

            ""
           /
         "("
        /   \
      "(("   "()"
       |      |
     "(()"   "()("
       |      |
    "(())"   "()()"
    

7️⃣ Complexity
Metric	Complexity
Time	O(4ⁿ / √n)
Space	O(n) recursion stack

This is related to Catalan numbers, which count valid parentheses combinations.

